entries.npc_11: Oh.  Well that figures.  He never did appreciate this baby.  That's why he lost her to me.
entries.npc_10: Well, if you find the guy that did tell him I'll take on any and all comers, you got it?
entries.npc_5: Nice?  Nice?  I can't believe this.  That's what you heard?  My ship is nice?  Who told you that?
entries.npc_9: I make a fair living.  Don't go spreading any rumors, you got me?
entries.player_8: The Kessel run?  Isn't that illegal?
entries.npc_8: Let's just say she's the fastest hunk of junk in the galaxy and leave it at that.
entries.player_7: No, really.  I'd like to hear it.
entries.npc_4: You're kidding.  It made the Kessel run in...ah forget it.
entries.player_5: Millenium Falcon?  Never heard of it.
entries.npc_3: That's right.  The Millenium Falcon.  Of course you already knew that.
entries.npc_7: Not a gangster eh?  Good for you.
entries.npc_6: The Hutt?  Lives on Tatooine?  Nevermind, if you don't know him then, yeah, I'm Han Solo.  Pleased to meet ya.
entries.npc_2: That depends.  You work for Jabba?
entries.player_2: I hear you've got a nice ship.
entries.npc_1: Something I can do for you?
